{"tid":284932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣東内地團GNZ48 啱香港人口味😍😍","createTime":"2017-06-15T10:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-15T18:05:20.000Z","uid":49648,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a6d9256e14a30cbfb0b1260496513f9a0a648ce","tid":284932,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/184933_52c5dca665f3e35dcad9c9d31a62256e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F184933_52c5dca665f3e35dcad9c9d31a62256e.jpg&h=6e52eca4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸真係好多女仔好正，港女不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170615/bkn-20170615154915470-0615_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170615%2Fbkn-20170615154915470-0615_00862_001.html&d=6wfPHStBatE9TzfwlFmcfTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=00c2bdbe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170615/bkn-20170615154915470-0615_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n內地組合GNZ48其中4名成員劉倩倩、唐莉佳、張凱祺及陳欣妤到電台宣傳第一首廣東歌《紫荊》，唐莉佳更即席自彈自唱《奇妙能量歌》。張凱祺指其他60位隊員在廣州工作和上課，她們平時要上舞蹈和聲樂課，會分成3隊，G隊有23人、N3隊有21人，Z隊有20人：「我哋運用日本組合嗰個模式，48系，同上海SH48、北京BJ48同瀋陽SHY48係姊妹團。」<br />\n<br />\n至於一班女生可會鬧交？張凱祺認為有鬧交是正常：「都係好小嘅磨擦，覺得一家人咁，我哋相處咗一、兩年。（為咩磨擦？）可能係關於舞蹈，我覺得呢個動作係咁樣做，佢又話唔係，不過最尾都會統一一個答案。」<br />\n<br />\n儲獎金吃火鍋<br />\n<br />\n陳欣妤指N3隊隊長劉倩倩負責管錢，隊員每次遲到要罰人民幣50元。張凱祺強調她們會盡量不遲到：「如果我哋全勤就有獎金，即係唔遲到、唔缺席，有500蚊人民幣，好多人攞過。（你哋四個有冇？）冇！」而被罰最多的成員今次沒有現身。問如何運用罰款？屬於G隊的張凱祺指她們會儲起，然後與隊員開Party聯絡感情，而屬於N3隊的另外3人就表示會吃火鍋。<br />\n<br />\n提到新EP《I.F》中的《紫荊》，張凱祺說紫荊花的花語是親情和兄弟情：「希望交畀大家有家嘅感覺，無論喺出面經歷幾多風風雨雨，聽到呢首歌都會感受到親情嘅溫暖。係抒情歌，有舞蹈。」"},{"pid":"e3cace2216e731a6d62c34204b46765e2ae406df","tid":284932,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:52:33.000Z","msg":"Bj48<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6deaf01537b1e4a20583c1714187030879742afc","tid":284932,"uid":5721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T10:56:34.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"8003091324d6c3b7ec2a4d595816f71d12789fa8","tid":284932,"uid":54183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:00:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5e33ff6df932c642fbd14de270e6085c8f62e6a","tid":284932,"uid":98692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:00:31.000Z","msg":"右一似男人"},{"pid":"f20d8d8153895ed648622e3f0e0fe93b7e95dcb4","tid":284932,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/190202_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F190202_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=05b1efad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1773b26d8c5b17b03c20a7ddafbcc99f91240cf","tid":284932,"uid":58456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"收皮啦仲用48個名"},{"pid":"9cc59abe82693ce27af0079070ebd841d31f15fa","tid":284932,"uid":56453,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:03:23.000Z","msg":"東莞女團？DGG48？"},{"pid":"158efab3eed2e7ccf1f4ff3bc5bf9568623a8ec9","tid":284932,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:05:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Bj48<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賓周刀損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e09fc8c8ffebb2b2b2f30b82e4d1e4f6deb3f3","tid":284932,"uid":71676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"